{"tid":1518130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：中共中央最高層否決撤回修例 下令林鄭不得回應任何訴求","createTime":"2019-08-30T06:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:25:47.000Z","uid":68738,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0e92239f6bacff2688e761316c1bfddbbe3cb2","tid":1518130,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190830/large/1567146449_4c43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190830%2Flarge%2F1567146449_4c43.jpg&h=94868f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首林鄭月娥一直不回應示威者提出的五大訴求。(路透社)<br />\n<br />\n香港逆權運動持續，路透社獨家引述消息報道，是中共中央政府最高層親自否決撤回《逃犯條例》修訂。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息報道，香港行政長官林鄭月娥在夏初曾向北京提交報告，當時評估過示威者五大訴求後，特區政府認為撤回《逃犯條例》修訂可以緩和香港局勢，但中共中央政府否決其建議，當時更命令她不得回應示威者的任何訴求。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指出，今次首次釐清北京在事件中的角色，並披露是北京拒絕林鄭就解決當前局勢的建議，形容反映「中國控制香港政府回應社會亂局程度」的實質證據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190830/59990230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59990230&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUinlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=1115b378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190830%2F59990230&h=66b2549d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190830/59990230</a>"},{"pid":"8b237cbfe400ffcfbe4cb444ba903f9dfa79b2b1","tid":1518130,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2